# Build context is the monorepo root for both Dockerfiles.
# NOTE: .env.prod is intentionally NOT ignored — the web build inlines
# NEXT_PUBLIC_* from it. Plain `.env` (dev) IS ignored to avoid interference.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.vercel
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development
**/.env.development.local
**/logs
.git
.github
deploy
nginx
minio_config
README.md
DEPLOYMENT.md
